437306AE.Line27.13C52A: Well, you need not go alone.

9270B1CA.Line25.BC41C: I led my soldiers into those damned ruins, and two of them lost their lives. Alim and Tala... I must retrieve their belongings.

C659A4CE.Line29.BC41C: Fine. I will accept your aid, wanderer. Meet me outside the old ruins to the west. And steel yourself for a fight.

F87C3848.Line23.BC41C: (sigh) A generous offer. But this is my responsibility.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “Where do you need to go? Perhaps I can help.”
